HEADWORD: Silverspot
<hw>Sil"ver*spot`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of numerous species of butterflies of the genus
<gen>Argynnis</gen> and allied genera, having silvery spots on the under
side of the wings..</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Silver State</ent>⟦br⟧
